Description.Desc:
Press <IconMap:Icon_Normal> to activate:
Perform up to five strikes forward, dealing <color=#FE437E>Ether DMG</color>;
The fifth attack is a <color=#FFFFFF>[Reverie]</color>, which manifests an Ethereal form to deal <color=#FE437E>Ether DMG</color> to enemies in a circular area ahead;
While in-combat and not in <color=#FFFFFF>[Dream]</color> state, Lucia gains 40 <color=#FFFFFF>[Dream Points]</color> when activating this <color=#FFFFFF>[Reverie]</color>.

Press <IconMap:Icon_Normal> during a <color=#FFFFFF>[Perfect Dodge]</color> to activate:
The Dodge Counter becomes <color=#FFFFFF>[Reverie]</color>, unleashing an Ethereal form downward attack in a circular area ahead, dealing <color=#FE437E>Ether DMG</color>;
When not in <color=#FFFFFF>[Dream]</color> state, Lucia gains 20 <color=#FFFFFF>[Dream Points]</color> when activating this <color=#FFFFFF>[Reverie]</color>, once every 5 seconds;
Character is invulnerable while using this skill.

Press <IconMap:Icon_Special> to activate:
Special Attack is <color=#FFFFFF>[Reverie]</color>, when activated, manifests an Ethereal form to perform a Slash attack in a line, dealing <color=#FE437E>Ether DMG</color>;
While in-combat and not in <color=#FFFFFF>[Dream]</color> state, when Lucia activates this <color=#FFFFFF>[Reverie]</color>, she gains 20 <color=#FFFFFF>[Dream Points]</color>, can only be gained once every 5 seconds.

With enough Energy, press <IconMap:Icon_SpecialReady> to activate:
EX Special Attack becomes <color=#FFFFFF>[Chorus]</color>, unleashing a powerful Ethereal slash in a line ahead, dealing <color=#FE437E>Ether DMG</color>;
When Lucia activates <color=#FFFFFF>[Chorus]</color>, applies <color=#FFFFFF>[Dark Break]</color> status to all squad members; Under <color=#FFFFFF>[Dark Break]</color>, Sheer Force increases by 300 points. When Lucia's initial max HP exceeds 9,000, every 250 points above increases Sheer Force by an additional 10 points. <color=#FFFFFF>[Dark Break]</color> can increase Sheer Force by up to {CAL:900+AvatarSkillLevel(1)*0,1,2} points and lasts 20 seconds, repeated triggers reset the duration;
When <color=#FFFFFF>[Chorus]</color> deals DMG, Lucia increases the final hit's DMG by <color=#2BAD00>{CAL:0.34+AvatarSkillLevel(1)*0.03,100,2}%</color> of her max HP;
When Lucia activates EX Special Attack while in <color=#FFFFFF>[Dream]</color> state and <color=#FFFFFF>[Ether Veil: Gushing Spring]</color> is active, extends <color=#FFFFFF>[Ether Veil: Gushing Spring]</color>'s duration by 12 seconds;
After activating EX Special Attack, Lucia can immediately follow up with the fifth hit of <color=#FFFFFF>[Basic Attack]</color>;
When not in <color=#FFFFFF>[Dream]</color> state, using this <color=#FFFFFF>[Chorus]</color> grants 60 <color=#FFFFFF>[Dream Points]</color>;
Character is invulnerable while using this skill.

When a <color=#FFFFFF>[Chain Attack]</color> is triggered, select the character to activate:
When the Chain Attack is <color=#FFFFFF>[Chorus]</color>, it summons an Ethereal form that pulls nearby enemies into a circular area and deals <color=#FE437E>Ether DMG</color>;
When not in <color=#FFFFFF>[Dream]</color> state, Lucia gains 40 <color=#FFFFFF>[Dream Points]</color> when activating this <color=#FFFFFF>[Chorus]</color>;
Character is invulnerable while using this skill.

When Decibel Rating reaches [Maximum], press <IconMap:Icon_UltimateReady> to activate:
Ultimate becomes <color=#FFFFFF>[Chorus]</color>. When activated, manifests the Ethereal form. Lucia mounts the Ethereal and charges forward. Hold directional buttons to control the riding direction and extend charge duration up to 3 seconds. During the charge, Anti-Interrupt Level increases, DMG taken is reduced by 40%, and Lucia cannot die, with HP dropping to no lower than 1;
When the charge ends, unleashes a powerful Strike in a large area dealing <color=#FE437E>Ether DMG</color> and creates a <color=#FFFFFF>[Starlight Convergence Field]</color>. <color=#FFFFFF>[Starlight Convergence Field]</color> lasts 8 seconds. Characters within the <color=#FFFFFF>[Starlight Convergence Field]</color> receive HP recovery: restoring <color=#2BAD00>{CAL:0.01+AvatarSkillLevel(3)*0.0005,100,2}%</color> of Lucia's max HP per second. This recovery effect disappears 4 seconds after leaving the <color=#FFFFFF>[Starlight Convergence Field]</color> or when leaving the field;
If Lucia is in <color=#FFFFFF>[Dreamstate]</color> and <color=#FFFFFF>[Ether Veil: Gushing Spring]</color> is active when activated, extends <color=#FFFFFF>[Ether Veil: Gushing Spring]</color>'s duration by 24 seconds;
When not in <color=#FFFFFF>[Dreamstate]</color>, Lucia gains 100 <color=#FFFFFF>[Dream Points]</color> upon activating this <color=#FFFFFF>[Chorus]</color>. If activated while in <color=#FFFFFF>[Dreamstate]</color>, Lucia will gain 100 <color=#FFFFFF>[Dream Points]</color> and re-enter <color=#FFFFFF>[Dreamstate]</color> the next time she exits <color=#FFFFFF>[Dreamstate]</color>. This effect cannot be gained repeatedly;
Character is invulnerable during the powerful Strike.

When the active character is launched, press <IconMap:Icon_Switch> to activate:
Quick Assist as <color=#FFFFFF>[Reverie]</color>, unleashing an Ethereal form to perform a downward attack in a circular area ahead, dealing <color=#FE437E>Ether DMG</color>;
When not in <color=#FFFFFF>[Dream]</color> state, Lucia gains 20 <color=#FFFFFF>[Dream Points]</color> when activating this <color=#FFFFFF>[Reverie]</color>, once every 5 seconds.;
Character is invulnerable while using this skill.

Press <IconMap:Icon_Normal> after a <color=#FFFFFF>[Defensive Assist]</color> to activate:
Assist Follow-Up becomes <color=#FFFFFF>[Chorus]</color>, unleashing a powerful downward attack in a circular area ahead in Ethereal form, dealing <color=#FE437E>Ether DMG</color>;
When not in <color=#FFFFFF>[Dream]</color> state, Lucia gains 40 <color=#FFFFFF>[Dream Points]</color> when activating this <color=#FFFFFF>[Chorus]</color>;
Character is invulnerable while using this skill.

Desc:
Upon entering the battlefield, Lucia immediately gains 60 <color=#FFFFFF>[Dream Value]</color>. When activating <color=#FFFFFF>[Reverie]</color> or <color=#FFFFFF>[Chorus]</color>, if Lucia's <color=#FFFFFF>[Dream Value]</color> reaches 100, she enters <color=#FFFFFF>[Dreamstate]</color> and activates <color=#FFFFFF>[Ether Veil: Gushing Spring]</color>. While <color=#FFFFFF>[Ether Veil: Gushing Spring]</color> is active, all squad members' max HP increases by 5%, lasting 30 seconds. Repeated triggers extend the duration, up to 300 seconds;
While Lucia is in <color=#FFFFFF>[Dreamstate]</color>, activating any <color=#FFFFFF>[Reverie]</color> consumes 25 <color=#FFFFFF>[Dream Value]</color> to upgrade <color=#FFFFFF>[Reverie]</color> to <color=#FFFFFF>[Chorus]</color>;
When in the background, if the active character's attacks hit enemies, Lucia consumes 25 <color=#FFFFFF>[Dream Value]</color> to trigger an <color=#FFFFFF>[Aftershock]</color>. The <color=#FFFFFF>[Aftershock]</color> is a <color=#FFFFFF>[Chorus]</color>. After triggering a skill upgrade or <color=#FFFFFF>[Aftershock]</color>, <color=#FFFFFF>[Aftershock]</color> cannot be triggered again for 6 seconds;
When Lucia triggers a skill upgrade or <color=#FFFFFF>[Aftershock]</color>, all squad members gain <color=#FFFFFF>[Dream Lullaby]</color> status. Under <color=#FFFFFF>[Dream Lullaby]</color> status, characters deal <color=#2BAD00>11.7%</color> more DMG for 8 seconds. Repeated triggers reset the duration;
Lucia exits <color=#FFFFFF>[Dreamstate]</color> when <color=#FFFFFF>[Dream Value]</color> is insufficient or when leaving <color=#FFFFFF>[Ether Veil]</color>.

